Player: I wouldn't have agreed to the alli...

He blinked, slightly taken aback.

Player: This isn't about me. This is about...

Player: No. Although God knows I've though...

Player: Never. I love my wife more than an...

en


He looked at me sternly.

en


He looked relieved.

en


He looked at me sadly.

en

"The tensions between Sordland and Rumburg have not eased. Quite the contrary."

Deivid Wisci: As you might imagine, our decision...

"As you might imagine, our decision to grant asylum to their whistleblower Mr. Hailstone did not sit well with the Kingdom."

Deivid Wisci: As you might imagine, the embargo...
